class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074bf0309668e0e1b087fa3a55e410b7161321d6","tid":1046354,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:15:32.000Z","msg":"值得一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b4d5eec6891c2d939237b26713529caea72a14","tid":1046354,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:17:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4010db79a9ac2f32f956ff39896892903a7ddfea","tid":1046354,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:34:00.000Z","msg":"中共：龍門任我搬！我鍾意點就點！吹咩！吹咩！"},{"pid":"a143c59cfe01fb86364a59b606ad6ab7c2eeb3c5","tid":1046354,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58976b33755f11f356c6f641e4ec2db850a88c99","tid":1046354,"uid":23180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:27:49.000Z","msg":"人治政權連證據都可以變出黎<br />\n<br />\n個問題根本唔係罪名輕重<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知所謂「香港法庭把關」可以憑咩推翻中國法庭嘅判決，家陣司法覆核已經一大堆話香港無權管嘅案已經有一大批<br />\n<br />\n作為外國公民係要擔心自己個下場有機會好似康明凱咁<br />\n<br />\n當你個主權國同共匪國有紛爭果陣無啦啦俾人拉兼用呢招做合法洗頭艇拉上去無限期監禁<br />\n<br />\n有d狗官就口口聲聲吹咩公義，明明有其他方法你唔做，係要攞香港個法律招牌黎較飛危害其他國家公民同香港人嘅人生安全，公義？俾人拉左上去無得保釋果班人有無人俾公義佢？<br />\n<br />\n叫人唔好政治化，諗下你自己個殖民主一路攞法庭黎做緊咩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964e5bc4625850defaea9db332d9766adcbf742d","tid":1046354,"uid":57413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:30:30.000Z","msg":"咁又可以點？阻止到咩？"},{"pid":"51f70e55d117d401806cdf8283cde0169e7228ec","tid":1046354,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},{"pid":"cf65d36687a4a6fb566de3a06bf028419c1a1c80","tid":1046354,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ec09baedacdb8bb1f287715a58a68d810b